articles.author: David Latona
articles.title: Spain's Princess Leonor swears allegiance to divided nation on her 18th birthday - Reuters
articles.description: Princess Leonor, the heir to Spain's throne, formally stepped into the spotlight by swearing allegiance to the constitution on her 18th birthday on Tuesday, though boycotts by leftist and separatist politicians underlined divisions over the monarchy.
